high_descs: Walk around the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Take a step to the left to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up the slice of potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk around the room to face the tall shelf structure.
Place the potato slice in the pot at the bottom of the shelves.
Pick up the Pot with the potato slice in it.
Walk around the room to face the fridge.
Place the pot with a potato slice in it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a potato slice in a pot plus move them to the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward, hang a left, go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is closest to the wall from the counter.
Turn to the right, go to the sink, hang a right, go to the counter between the sink and coffee maker.
Cut the potato that is on the counter into slices.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn to the left, go to the counter that is between the sink and coffee maker.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a left, go to the brown shelves at the end of the room on the right.
Put the potato into the pot that is on the second shelf.
Pick up the pot containing the potato from the shelf.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left, go to the counter, hang a right and go to the fridge.
Put the pot on the middle shelf inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing potato inside the fridge.
